      <odd id="aspace_b93cc74ddf2e5d38eb1187ef56180976">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 32-B (YRG 32-B), Records of deputy, associate, and assistant university librarians of Yale University.</p>  
      </odd>
